OL,3,CMan backs fundraiser for new 'cuddle
OL,4,Cbed' for St Luke's Hospice in Winsford
OL,5,Cwhere wife died
OL,7,FThe widow of a woman who died while in
OL,8,Fthe care of their local hospice has
OL,9,Fbacked a fundraiser to buy a new
OL,10,F#12,000 "cuddle bed" for the in-
OL,11,Fpatients unit.
OL,13,FMike Summersgill's wife Sue, 52, died
OL,14,Fat St Luke's Hospice, in Winsford, in
OL,15,FOctober 2023 after she was diagnosed
OL,16,Fwith terminal cancer.
OL,18,FDuring those precious final weeks, the
OL,19,Fhospice provided their one and only
OL,20,F"cuddle bed" for the couple, from
OL,21,FCrewe, who were married 26 years.
